  "description": "Highlight changes the visualization of specific blocks in the game to have more aligned selections to their models.",
  "body": "<img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Highlight/BH_H_Title.png\">\n<p></p>\n<img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Highlight/BH_H_Overview.png\">\n<p></p>\n<center><p>This mod changes the visualization of specific blocks in the game that generally would have axis-bound selection boxes to have angled selection boxes to match their model and generally improve the look of the block.</p></center>\n<p></p>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/34ZhTuy.png\">\n<p></p>\n<a href=\"https://resourceful-bees.gitbook.io/resourceful-lib/highlights\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Highlight/BH_H_Wiki.png\"></a>\n<p></p>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/resourcefulbees\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Highlight/BH_H_Discord.png\"></a>\n<p></p>\n<a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/teamresourceful\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Highlight/BH_H_BisectPromo.png\"></a>",
